:68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:45:37.000Z","msg":"秋天快到 安全第一<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小心山火</span></span>"},{"pid":"15039a928f9fb7487a230337586651a9389e8e95","tid":1352553,"uid":80725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:46:50.000Z","msg":"屯元天 <br />\n如果唔出<br />\n下一次可能係天水圍 屯門 恐襲"},{"pid":"42d63fac90ceefab6c27b28c56a70eacbc4cdb00","tid":1352553,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:49:32.000Z","msg":"快啲出文宣<br />\n時間無多"},{"pid":"b4024e90223da174625d8d3f63b0309a4754404f","tid":1352553,"uid":203933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:51:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d060fd633bae6296bb6d51093ccf725962698f4","tid":1352553,"uid":277589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:54:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48a400749ba1680255185edff073de180915b11e","tid":1352553,"uid":12994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:03:35.000Z","msg":"因為如果示威者都無反抗<br />\n下次班牛屎佬咪可以繼續<br />\n而家根本就搵緊第三方既野收示威者皮<br />\n爛頭卒都唔敢出黎 下次咪無人可以搵<br />\n重係咁叫人唔好入元朗<br />\n屌你老味係咪香港人黎<br />\n比人打到豬頭重叫睇定啲先<br />\n你老母人多入到去 <br />\n再行高速公路過大欖落荃灣都得啦<br />\n最重要人多 其他驚西咩"},{"pid":"b7a1d16851eb390d47f013ccb6f4c51e78839e7c","tid":1352553,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:07:55.000Z","msg":"727"},{"pid":"f29bc345abb48f691ebe746e86785eaafd9f1cec","tid":1352553,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"唔係唔去<br />\n用咩名義行咩路線先最重要"},{"pid":"d73a7539358cfbe19b37c441730cb3b87c8bfe2f","tid":1352553,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要去<br />\n去左先可以破解而家嘅白色恐怖<br />\n唔係嘅話依種白色恐怖會蔓延全港<br />\n到時就真係玩完<br />\n個多月黎嘅烈士同義士就白白犧牲<br />\n<br />\n今次去你唔使驚<br />\n因為今次一定有好多國際媒體、日韓、台灣媒體會去<br />\n21號外地媒體佢地自己都始料不及北區會咁大鑊<br />\n今次知左嘅話一定睇住個場<br />\n<br />\n兼扯圍村仔警署二哥鄧炳強如果係黎緊嘅遊行又搞事<br />\n佢今次紮唔到一哥個位<br />\n會被競爭對手郭sir取而代之<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要去！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b77f396d04251bd9da2338bf0c84c2d4c4ff3a96","tid":1352553,"uid":59700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T00:21:13.000Z","msg":"亂咁打人 我地去教返好元朗人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}